org.wiyn.etc.configuration
Class GenericProperties

java.lang.Object
  org.wiyn.etc.configuration.GenericProperties
All Implemented Interfaces:
AllowingPropertyChanges
Direct Known Subclasses:
LunarProperties, SolarProperties, TelescopeProperties
public class GenericProperties
extends java.lang.Object
implements AllowingPropertyChanges

This is the superclass of all the classes describing RSS related properties. It provides the methods for adding and removing property change listeners and for firing property change events.
